In Belgium, similarities between Dutch and French words often lead to confusion when several different meanings of the same word are mixed up and thus mistranslated. In satirical sketch comedy ''Sois Belge et tais-toi!'', performed by Joël Riguelle in 2009, the following examples are given:<ref>Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6mwIutXeHxE |title=Sois Belge Et Tais-toi 2009 - Derde Les |author=Joël Riguelle |work=Sois Belge Et Tais-toi 2009 |date=2009 |accessdate=28 January 2019 |language=fr</ref> 

